reportColumnMetadata.name: Period
reportColumnMetadata.description: Period

reportColumnMetadata.name: Name
reportColumnMetadata.description: Name

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total incoming
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total incoming
Total number of incoming calls.
Composed of: Incoming (external), Incoming (internal)
Composed of: Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other)
Composed of: Incoming (from queues)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Incoming (external)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Incoming (external)
Incoming calls from external numbers.
Included in: Total incoming - (Incoming (external), Incoming (internal))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Incoming (internal)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Incoming (internal)
Incoming calls from internal numbers/users.
Included in: Total incoming - (Incoming (external), Incoming (internal))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Incoming (from queues)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Incoming (from queues)
The number of calls that have been distributed to the user(s) from a queue where the user was a member.
Calls from hunt groups are not included in this value.
Included in: Total incoming - (Incoming (from queues), )

reportColumnMetadata.name: Answered
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Answered
Total number of answered calls. Calls answered by the voicemail are not included, see the column Redirected (voicemail).
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Unanswered
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Unanswered
Total number of calls where the caller did not receive any answer at all. Calls that have received a busy tone are not included, see the column Busy.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Busy
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Busy
Number of calls that received a busy tone.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total redirected
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total redirected
Total number of incoming calls that have been redirected to another number or to voicemail.
Composed of: Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Redirected (voicemail)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Redirected (voicemail)
Number of incoming calls that have been redirected to voicemail.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other)) Total redirected - (Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Redirected (to other)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Redirected (to other)
Number of incoming calls that have been redirected to another number. This value contains all redirected calls whether they have been answered or abandoned after the redirect.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered, Unanswered, Busy, Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other)) Total redirected - (Redirected (voicemail), Redirected (to other))

reportColumnMetadata.name: (Avg) Speed of answer
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(Avg) Speed of answer
The average time incoming calls have waited before being answered. This value is only based on the wait time for answered calls.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Incoming (Avg) Duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(Avg) Duration
The average call duration for incoming calls.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Incoming duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total duration
The total call duration for all incoming calls.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total outgoing
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total outgoing
Total number of outgoing calls.
Composed of: Outgoing (external), Outgoing (internal)
Composed of: Outgoing (answered), Outgoing (unanswered)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (external)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (external)
Outgoing calls to external numbers.
Included in: Total outgoing - (Outgoing (external), Outgoing (internal))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (internal)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (internal)
Outgoing calls to internal numbers/users.
Included in: Total outgoing - (Outgoing (external), Outgoing (internal))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (answered)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (answered)
Number of outgoing calls that have been answered.
Included in: Total outgoing - (Outgoing (answered), Outgoing (unanswered))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (unanswered)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (abandoned)
Number of outgoing calls that have not been answered.
Included in: Total outgoing - (Outgoing (answered), Outgoing (unanswered))

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (busy)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (busy)
Outgoing calls that have received a busy tone.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing (Avg) Duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing (Avg) Duration
The average call duration for outgoing calls.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Outgoing duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Outgoing duration
The total call duration for all outgoing calls.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Transferred out
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Transferred out
Number of incoming calls that have been manually transported. These calls are not included in the column Total outgoing.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total calls (in/out)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total calls (in/out)
The total number of calls, both incoming and outgoing.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total call duration (in/out)
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total call duration (in/out)
The total call duration for all calls, both incoming and outgoing.

reportColumnMetadata.name: (%) Answered
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(%) Answered
Percentage of all incoming calls that have been answered. (This value does not contain calls that have been redirected and answered in the next step).

reportColumnMetadata.name: Failure
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Failure
Number of call attempts (both in and out) that have been cancelled because of failure.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Group names
reportColumnMetadata.description: The names of the groups the object or group belong to

reportColumnMetadata.name: Object identifier
reportColumnMetadata.description: The unique identifier of the object the row represents

reportColumnMetadata.name: Type
reportColumnMetadata.description: Describes if the row represent the total, a group or a an object.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Depth in hierarchy
reportColumnMetadata.description: The level of the object/group is in the hierarchy. Indicates how many parent groups the object/group has.
